data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  This beautiful, move-in ready, single-story Covina home on a large lot. The inviting floor plan flows from living room to dining area and kitchen.  Kitchen layout provides lots of counter space and storage and includes stainless steel appliances. Living room is large and inviting with windows that bring in natural light and provide views of the spacious backyard.  Three bedrooms are well sized and have their own a/c units. Bathroom has updated tub and shower surround. Laundry area is conveniently located in the insulated garage with direct access from kitchen.  Attached garage has endless possibilities and provides additional attic storage.  Lot is almost 8,000 square feet.  Plenty of room to expand.  Covered patio, fruit trees, dog area and custom storage shed. Other updates include upgraded electrical panel and subpanel, new wall heater installed in 2020, new water softener system, newer roof, solar tubes for additional natural light, ceiling fans, and security camera on front door.
